		"description": "<p>This bag of consecrated salt can be spread onto up to 2 spaces adjacent to the user as an action. Undead, fiends, and aberrations treat a space covered with holy salt as difficult terrain and take 2d4 points of radiant damage the first time on a turn they enter such a space or when they start their turn there. The salt retains its potency for up to 8 hours. Adding another application of holy salt to a space already occupied by holy salt resets the duration, but produces no additional effect.</p>",
